          {
            "md": "**CC.A.4A.1** <u>Scope</u>",
            "value": "CC.A.4A.1 <u>Scope</u>",
            "bbox": [
              {
                "h": 10.238189576981704,
                "w": 99.83774614138721,
                "x": 42.03757274199696,
                "y": 225.5881465129573,
                "confidence": 0.87,
                "end_index": 25,
                "label": "paragraph_title",
                "start_index": 0
              }
            ],
            "type": "text"
          },
          {
            "md": "The fault ride through requirement is defined in CC.6.3.15.1 (a), (b) and CC.6.3.15.3. This Appendix provides illustrations by way of examples only of CC.6.3.15.1 (a) (i) and further background and illustrations to CC.6.3.15.1 (1b) (i) and CC.6.3.15.1 (2b) (i) and is not intended to show all possible permutations.",
            "value": "The fault ride through requirement is defined in CC.6.3.15.1 (a), (b) and CC.6.3.15.3. This Appendix provides illustrations by way of examples only of CC.6.3.15.1 (a) (i) and further background and illustrations to CC.6.3.15.1 (1b) (i) and CC.6.3.15.1 (2b) (i) and is not intended to show all possible permutations.",
            "bbox": [
              {
                "h": 48.939006402439055,
                "w": 413.5420792682928,
                "x": 112.38550266768296,
                "y": 244.15737653391767,
                "confidence": 0.98,
                "end_index": 314,
                "label": "text",
                "start_index": 0
              }
            ],
            "type": "text"
          },
          {
            "md": "**CC.A.4A.2** <u>Short Circuit Faults At Supergrid Voltage On The Onshore Transmission System Up To 140ms In Duration</u>",
            "value": "CC.A.4A.2 <u>Short Circuit Faults At Supergrid Voltage On The Onshore Transmission System Up To 140ms In Duration</u>",
            "bbox": [
              {
                "h": 23.19177870617383,
                "w": 484.56884451219526,
                "x": 41.957708460365865,
                "y": 313.3105895579268,
                "confidence": 0.88,
                "end_index": 120,
                "label": "paragraph_title",
                "start_index": 0
              }
            ],
            "type": "text"
          },
          {
            "md": "For short circuit faults at **Supergrid Voltage** on the **Onshore Transmission System** (which could be at an **Interface Point**) up to 140ms in duration, the fault ride through requirement is defined in CC.6.3.15.1 (a) (i). Figures CC.A.4A.1 (a) and (b) illustrate two typical examples of voltage recovery for short-circuit faults cleared within 140ms by two circuit breakers (a) and three circuit breakers (b) respectively.",
            "value": "For short circuit faults at Supergrid Voltage on the Onshore Transmission System (which could be at an Interface Point) up to 140ms in duration, the fault ride through requirement is defined in CC.6.3.15.1 (a) (i). Figures CC.A.4A.1 (a) and (b) illustrate two typical examples of voltage recovery for short-circuit faults cleared within 140ms by two circuit breakers (a) and three circuit breakers (b) respectively.",
